WEBVTT



00:00:00.864 --> 00:00:04.992
This sermon is brought to you by Buford Road Baptist Church.

00:00:04.768 --> 00:00:08.160
the speaker today is Pastor Tony Kahoot

00:00:08.832 --> 00:00:11.584
I want to share just a little thought with you.

00:00:11.680 --> 00:00:17.728
From yesterday's funeral. I don't know if anybody's here, as I've already mentioned, from that.

00:00:17.824 --> 00:00:21.120
Service, but as I was sitting in the chair and.

00:00:21.184 --> 00:00:28.480
There were so many people that they had opened the floor up to whoever wanted to say anything could come up here.

00:00:28.288 --> 00:00:31.104
One after the other did, and I sat there and.

00:00:31.328 --> 00:00:32.224
Uh,

00:00:32.064 --> 00:00:35.232
I said, Lord, there's no way.

00:00:35.808 --> 00:00:38.336
That I can preach this message.

00:00:39.328 --> 00:00:42.784
And it was almost like the Lord said, I know that.

00:00:44.128 --> 00:00:50.944
And it had gone on for a little extended period of time. I said, these people are tired. They're sitting here.

00:00:50.816 --> 00:01:00.160
They've been they've been here for a while, and they've listened to these wonderful, beautiful, incredible stories. I said, they're not going to have their minds on the word at all.

00:00:59.808 --> 00:01:05.600
everybody's waiting to get out of here is pouring down rain and lark was just saying chill man chill.

00:01:08.672 --> 00:01:11.008
I said give me something Lord this

00:01:11.040 --> 00:01:14.304
Sermon I have is not going to work at this moment.

00:01:15.104 --> 00:01:20.544
And the Lord spoke to my heart. I think I have told you that the funeral yesterday was a

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:25.408
Four young men that had taken his life, tragically, a few days before Christmas,

00:01:25.728 --> 00:01:27.008
And so,

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:31.296
I had never done this before. In 40 plus years of preaching, I have never, never, never,

00:01:31.232 --> 00:01:34.368
Addressed suicide from a

00:01:34.272 --> 00:01:35.808
Straight up.

00:01:35.968 --> 00:01:37.856
Biblical perspective.

00:01:38.432 --> 00:01:41.088
And the Lord said, do it.

00:01:41.856 --> 00:01:43.264
And I did.

00:01:43.488 --> 00:01:46.080
And he gave me a just.

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:47.296
Two scriptures.

00:01:48.224 --> 00:01:50.720
And I presented it in such a way.

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:53.120
That in the end,

00:01:53.504 --> 00:01:57.088
16 people gave their hearts to Christ.

00:01:58.272 --> 00:02:00.672
At the conclusion of that sermon,

00:02:01.024 --> 00:02:06.656
I noticed down here at the front there was a young man that had fallen on the altar.

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:11.584
And there have been, listen, there has been a long time.

00:02:11.968 --> 00:02:14.944
Since I have seen tear stains.

00:02:15.392 --> 00:02:16.992
Only altar.

00:02:18.112 --> 00:02:20.160
Well, that ought to convict us.

00:02:21.184 --> 00:02:24.032
It ought to bring deep conviction to us.

00:02:25.024 --> 00:02:28.896
But I saw tear stains on the on the carpet.

00:02:29.504 --> 00:02:32.480
And I saw his body jerkin'.

00:02:34.144 --> 00:02:38.944
I stopped in the midst of the crowd. I went over there, put my arms around me. I said,

00:02:38.976 --> 00:02:41.024
I want to pray with your son

00:02:41.216 --> 00:02:43.936
His father had just taken his life.

00:02:44.736 --> 00:02:53.088
And he sobbed uncontrollably on this altar. I don't know what business he was doing with God, but I know something spiritual was going on.

00:02:53.824 --> 00:02:56.096
All I could do was pray with him.

00:02:56.832 --> 00:02:59.456
And I'll tell you all of that to say this.

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:03.072
Don't ever pass up an opportunity

00:03:03.456 --> 00:03:06.176
There'll be an instrument of the Lord.

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:16.416
The Bible says in Galatians Sixteen, as we have therefore opportunity, let us do good unto all men, especially unto them who are the household of faith.

00:03:17.184 --> 00:03:22.112
Don't pass your opportunities up because they may never come your way again.

00:03:22.816 --> 00:03:26.784
But I rejoice in the Lord for these twenty people that gave

00:03:26.752 --> 00:03:28.640
their hearts to Christ.

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:32.320
you listen to Pastor Tony Kahoot

00:03:32.224 --> 00:03:38.336
For more information, visit our website at bufordrodebaptistchurch.com
